"be mounted <a href='#/storage/filesystems/mount'>here</a>. For the latter, "
"please <a href='#/storage/disks'>wipe</a> the device as partitions are not "
"supported."
msgstr ""
"如果设备未在此处列出，通常是因为该设备已包含文件系统或分区。对于前者，文件系统可以在<a "
"href='#/storage/filesystems/mount'>此处</a>挂载。对于后者，请<a "
"href='#/storage/disks'>擦除</a>设备，因为分区不被支持。"

